com.github.epadronu.balin.config

Class ConfigurationBuilder

  • com.github.epadronu.balin.config.ConfigurationBuilder

  • public class ConfigurationBuilder

    Defines the builder used in the configuration DSL that can be interacted with via the Browser.Companion.configure method.

    val desiredConfigurationSetup = Configuration(false, testFactory)

Browser.configure {
    autoQuit = desiredConfigurationSetup.autoQuit

    driverFactory = desiredConfigurationSetup.driverFactory
}

Assert.assertEquals(Browser.desiredConfiguration, desiredConfigurationSetup)

    See Also:
    Browser.Companion.configure, interface ConfigurationSetup
